{"id": "figure_014", "modality": "figures", "name": "Seq2Seq with Attention + Attention Heat-Map Grid", "task": {"description": "Create a single 1920x1080 self-contained HTML file using ONLY inline CSS and inline SVG that reproduces a sequence-to-sequence with attention figure including an alignment heat-map. Title 'Seq2Seq with Attention' at top in 32px bold. BOTTOM-LEFT: an encoder RNN drawn as a horizontal row of FOUR recurrent cells over source tokens ('le','chat','est','noir') with left-to-right hidden-state arrows h_1..h_4. TOP/RIGHT: a decoder RNN drawn as a horizontal row of FOUR recurrent cells generating target tokens ('the','cat','is','black'). For the CURRENT decoder step draw attention weight arrows from ALL four encoder hidden states into a 'context vector c_t = \u03a3 \u03b1_ti h_i' node feeding the decoder cell. SEPARATELY, on the RIGHT, draw a 4 x 4 attention heat-map grid (source tokens on one axis, target tokens on the other) with cells shaded by attention weight and a roughly-diagonal alignment highlighted. Label the source axis and target axis of the heat-map. Four encoder cells, four decoder cells, 4x4 alignment grid. HARDEN (density + alignment): ALSO include (a) a LEGEND box that maps every distinct block color and every arrow/line style used in the figure, and (b) a small tensor-shape annotation on each major block (e.g. 'BxNxd'). Pack the figure densely with at least 14 labeled elements; every group of sibling blocks must be equal-size and share edges, with uniform gutters, and nothing may overlap or clip.", "requirements": ["The encoder row (4 cells), decoder row (4 cells), context-vector node, and 4x4 attention heat-map are all visible with no clipping at any edge", "No two cells/boxes overlap each other", "Every token label and cell label is fully contained inside its box with no overflow", "The encoder has EXACTLY four cells over the four source tokens and the decoder has EXACTLY four cells over the four target tokens", "Attention weight arrows from all four encoder hidden states feed into the context-vector node, which feeds the decoder", "The attention heat-map is a 4x4 grid (matching the 4 source and 4 target tokens) with cells shaded by weight", "The heat-map's source axis and target axis are both labelled with the correct token lists", "A roughly-diagonal alignment is visibly highlighted in the heat-map cells", "Encoder hidden-state arrows h_1..h_4 do not cross through unrelated cells", "Heat-map cells are evenly sized and evenly spaced (uniform grid)", "No element is within 10px of any viewport edge", "No horizontal or vertical scrollbar appears; all content fits inside 1920x1080", "A legend box maps every block color and arrow/line style used; each major block carries a tensor-shape annotation; sibling blocks are equal-size and edge-aligned with uniform gutters; no element overlaps or is clipped"]}, "runs": [{"run": 1, "ss_n_defects": 1, "ss_text_overlap": 1, "ss_clipped": 0, "ss_overflow": 0, "ss_total_tokens": 7601, "rv_n_defects": 0, "rv_text_overlap": 0, "rv_clipped": 0, "rv_overflow": 0, "rv_iterations": 1, "rv_total_tokens": 7989}, {"run": 2, "ss_n_defects": 0, "ss_text_overlap": 0, "ss_clipped": 0, "ss_overflow": 0, "ss_total_tokens": 8086, "rv_n_defects": 0, "rv_text_overlap": 0, "rv_clipped": 0, "rv_overflow": 0, "rv_iterations": 2, "rv_total_tokens": 22961}, {"run": 3, "ss_n_defects": 0, "ss_text_overlap": 0, "ss_clipped": 0, "ss_overflow": 0, "ss_total_tokens": 7490, "rv_n_defects": 0, "rv_text_overlap": 0, "rv_clipped": 0, "rv_overflow": 0, "rv_iterations": 2, "rv_total_tokens": 19536}], "ss_img": "images/figures/figure_014_ss.jpg", "rv_img": "images/figures/figure_014_rv.jpg", "ss_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Seq2Seq with Attention</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 20px;\n            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n            background: #f8f9fa;\n            width: 1880px;\n            height: 1040px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        .title {\n            font-size: 32px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            text-align: center;\n            color: #2c3e50;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"title\">Seq2Seq with Attention</div>\n    \n    <svg width=\"1880\" height=\"980\" viewBox=\"0 0 1880 980\">\n        <!-- Definitions for gradients and patterns -->\n        <defs>\n            <linearGradient id=\"encoderGrad\" x1=\"0%\" y1=\"0%\" x2=\"100%\" y2=\"100%\">\n                <stop offset=\"0%\" style=\"stop-color:#3498db;stop-opacity:1\" />\n                <stop offset=\"100%\" style=\"stop-color:#2980b9;stop-opacity:1\" />\n            </linearGradient>\n            <linearGradient id=\"decoderGrad\" x1=\"0%\" y1=\"0%\" x2=\"100%\" y2=\"100%\">\n                <stop offset=\"0%\" style=\"stop-color:#e74c3c;stop-opacity:1\" />\n                <stop offset=\"100%\" style=\"stop-color:#c0392b;stop-opacity:1\" />\n            </linearGradient>\n            <linearGradient id=\"contextGrad\" x1=\"0%\" y1=\"0%\" x2=\"100%\" y2=\"100%\">\n                <stop offset=\"0%\" style=\"stop-color:#f39c12;stop-opacity:1\" />\n                <stop offset=\"100%\" style=\"stop-color:#e67e22;stop-opacity:1\" />\n            </linearGradient>\n            <marker id=\"arrowhead\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#34495e\" />\n            </marker>\n            <marker id=\"attentionArrow\" markerWidth=\"8\" markerHeight=\"6\" refX=\"7\" refY=\"3\" orient=\"auto\">\n                <polygon points=\"0 0, 8 3, 0 6\" fill=\"#9b59b6\" />\n            </marker>\n        </defs>\n\n        <!-- Encoder Section -->\n        <g id=\"encoder\">\n            <!-- Encoder Label -->\n            <text x=\"300\" y=\"680\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"18\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Encoder RNN</text>\n            \n            <!-- Source tokens -->\n            <rect x=\"80\" y=\"720\" width=\"60\" height=\"30\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n            <text x=\"110\" y=\"740\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">le</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"180\" y=\"720\" width=\"60\" height=\"30\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n            <text x=\"210\" y=\"740\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">chat</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"280\" y=\"720\" width=\"60\" height=\"30\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n            <text x=\"310\" y=\"740\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">est</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"380\" y=\"720\" width=\"60\" height=\"30\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n            <text x=\"410\" y=\"740\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">noir</text>\n            \n            <!-- Encoder cells -->\n            <rect x=\"80\" y=\"780\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" fill=\"url(#encoderGrad)\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n            <text x=\"110\" y=\"805\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">RNN</text>\n            <text x=\"110\" y=\"820\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"white\">1x256</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"180\" y=\"780\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" fill=\"url(#encoderGrad)\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n            <text x=\"210\" y=\"805\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">RNN</text>\n            <text x=\"210\" y=\"820\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"white\">1x256</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"280\" y=\"780\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" fill=\"url(#encoderGrad)\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n            <text x=\"310\" y=\"805\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">RNN</text>\n            <text x=\"310\" y=\"820\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"white\">1x256</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"380\" y=\"780\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" fill=\"url(#encoderGrad)\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n            <text x=\"410\" y=\"805\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">RNN</text>\n            <text x=\"410\" y=\"820\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"white\">1x256</text>\n            \n            <!-- Hidden state arrows -->\n            <line x1=\"140\" y1=\"810\" x2=\"170\" y2=\"810\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <text x=\"155\" y=\"805\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#34495e\">h\u2081</text>\n            \n            <line x1=\"240\" y1=\"810\" x2=\"270\" y2=\"810\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <text x=\"255\" y=\"805\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#34495e\">h\u2082</text>\n            \n            <line x1=\"340\" y1=\"810\" x2=\"370\" y2=\"810\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <text x=\"355\" y=\"805\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#34495e\">h\u2083</text>\n            \n            <!-- Hidden state labels -->\n            <text x=\"110\" y=\"870\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#34495e\">h\u2081</text>\n            <text x=\"210\" y=\"870\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#34495e\">h\u2082</text>\n            <text x=\"310\" y=\"870\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#34495e\">h\u2083</text>\n            <text x=\"410\" y=\"870\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#34495e\">h\u2084</text>\n        </g>\n\n        <!-- Context Vector -->\n        <g id=\"context\">\n            <rect x=\"600\" y=\"400\" width=\"120\" height=\"80\" fill=\"url(#contextGrad)\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"3\" rx=\"10\"/>\n            <text x=\"660\" y=\"425\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">Context</text>\n            <text x=\"660\" y=\"445\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"white\">c_t = \u03a3 \u03b1_ti h_i</text>\n            <text x=\"660\" y=\"465\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"white\">1x256</text>\n        </g>\n\n        <!-- Attention arrows from encoder to context -->\n        <line x1=\"110\" y1=\"780\" x2=\"620\" y2=\"480\" stroke=\"#9b59b6\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#attentionArrow)\" stroke-dasharray=\"5,3\"/>\n        <line x1=\"210\" y1=\"780\" x2=\"640\" y2=\"480\" stroke=\"#9b59b6\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#attentionArrow)\"/>\n        <line x1=\"310\" y1=\"780\" x2=\"660\" y2=\"480\" stroke=\"#9b59b6\" stroke-width=\"4\" marker-end=\"url(#attentionArrow)\"/>\n        <line x1=\"410\" y1=\"780\" x2=\"680\" y2=\"480\" stroke=\"#9b59b6\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#attentionArrow)\" stroke-dasharray=\"5,3\"/>\n\n        <!-- Decoder Section -->\n        <g id=\"decoder\">\n            <!-- Decoder Label -->\n            <text x=\"660\" y=\"180\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"18\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Decoder RNN</text>\n            \n            <!-- Decoder cells -->\n            <rect x=\"480\" y=\"200\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" fill=\"url(#decoderGrad)\" stroke=\"#c0392b\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n            <text x=\"510\" y=\"225\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">RNN</text>\n            <text x=\"510\" y=\"240\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"white\">1x256</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"580\" y=\"200\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" fill=\"url(#decoderGrad)\" stroke=\"#c0392b\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n            <text x=\"610\" y=\"225\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">RNN</text>\n            <text x=\"610\" y=\"240\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"white\">1x256</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"680\" y=\"200\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" fill=\"url(#decoderGrad)\" stroke=\"#c0392b\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n            <text x=\"710\" y=\"225\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">RNN</text>\n            <text x=\"710\" y=\"240\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"white\">1x256</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"780\" y=\"200\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" fill=\"url(#decoderGrad)\" stroke=\"#c0392b\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n            <text x=\"810\" y=\"225\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">RNN</text>\n            <text x=\"810\" y=\"240\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"white\">1x256</text>\n            \n            <!-- Target tokens -->\n            <rect x=\"480\" y=\"120\" width=\"60\" height=\"30\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n            <text x=\"510\" y=\"140\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">the</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"580\" y=\"120\" width=\"60\" height=\"30\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n            <text x=\"610\" y=\"140\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">cat</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"680\" y=\"120\" width=\"60\" height=\"30\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n            <text x=\"710\" y=\"140\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">is</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"780\" y=\"120\" width=\"60\" height=\"30\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n            <text x=\"810\" y=\"140\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">black</text>\n            \n            <!-- Decoder hidden state arrows -->\n            <line x1=\"540\" y1=\"230\" x2=\"570\" y2=\"230\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <line x1=\"640\" y1=\"230\" x2=\"670\" y2=\"230\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <line x1=\"740\" y1=\"230\" x2=\"770\" y2=\"230\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Output arrows -->\n            <line x1=\"510\" y1=\"200\" x2=\"510\" y2=\"160\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <line x1=\"610\" y1=\"200\" x2=\"610\" y2=\"160\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <line x1=\"710\" y1=\"200\" x2=\"710\" y2=\"160\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <line x1=\"810\" y1=\"200\" x2=\"810\" y2=\"160\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        </g>\n\n        <!-- Context to current decoder step -->\n        <line x1=\"660\" y1=\"400\" x2=\"710\" y2=\"260\" stroke=\"#f39c12\" stroke-width=\"4\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n\n        <!-- Attention Heatmap -->\n        <g id=\"heatmap\">\n            <text x=\"1200\" y=\"180\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"18\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Attention Weights</text>\n            \n            <!-- Heatmap grid -->\n            <!-- Row 1 -->\n            <rect x=\"1000\" y=\"220\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#e8f5e8\" stroke=\"#27ae60\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n            <text x=\"1030\" y=\"255\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">0.1</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"1060\" y=\"220\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#fff3cd\" stroke=\"#f39c12\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n            <text x=\"1090\" y=\"255\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">0.2</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"1120\" y=\"220\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#f8d7da\" stroke=\"#e74c3c\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n            <text x=\"1150\" y=\"255\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">0.05</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"1180\" y=\"220\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#e8f5e8\" stroke=\"#27ae60\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n            <text x=\"1210\" y=\"255\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">0.1</text>\n            \n            <!-- Row 2 -->\n            <rect x=\"1000\" y=\"280\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#f8d7da\" stroke=\"#e74c3c\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n            <text x=\"1030\" y=\"315\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">0.05</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"1060\" y=\"280\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#d1ecf1\" stroke=\"#17a2b8\" stroke-width=\"3\"/>\n            <text x=\"1090\" y=\"315\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">0.8</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"1120\" y=\"280\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#fff3cd\" stroke=\"#f39c12\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n            <text x=\"1150\" y=\"315\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">0.3</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"1180\" y=\"280\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#f8d7da\" stroke=\"#e74c3c\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n            <text x=\"1210\" y=\"315\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">0.05</text>\n            \n            <!-- Row 3 -->\n            <rect x=\"1000\" y=\"340\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#f8d7da\" stroke=\"#e74c3c\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n            <text x=\"1030\" y=\"375\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">0.1</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"1060\" y=\"340\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#fff3cd\" stroke=\"#f39c12\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n            <text x=\"1090\" y=\"375\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">0.2</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"1120\" y=\"340\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#d1ecf1\" stroke=\"#17a2b8\" stroke-width=\"3\"/>\n            <text x=\"1150\" y=\"375\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">0.7</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"1180\" y=\"340\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#fff3cd\" stroke=\"#f39c12\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n            <text x=\"1210\" y=\"375\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">0.3</text>\n            \n            <!-- Row 4 -->\n            <rect x=\"1000\" y=\"400\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#e8f5e8\" stroke=\"#27ae60\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n            <text x=\"1030\" y=\"435\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">0.1</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"1060\" y=\"400\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#f8d7da\" stroke=\"#e74c3c\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n            <text x=\"1090\" y=\"435\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">0.1</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"1120\" y=\"400\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#fff3cd\" stroke=\"#f39c12\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n            <text x=\"1150\" y=\"435\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">0.2</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"1180\" y=\"400\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#d1ecf1\" stroke=\"#17a2b8\" stroke-width=\"3\"/>\n            <text x=\"1210\" y=\"435\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">0.9</text>\n            \n            <!-- Axis labels -->\n            <text x=\"950\" y=\"255\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">the</text>\n            <text x=\"950\" y=\"315\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">cat</text>\n            <text x=\"950\" y=\"375\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">is</text>\n            <text x=\"950\" y=\"435\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">black</text>\n            \n            <text x=\"1030\" y=\"210\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">le</text>\n            <text x=\"1090\" y=\"210\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">chat</text>\n            <text x=\"1150\" y=\"210\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">est</text>\n            <text x=\"1210\" y=\"210\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">noir</text>\n            \n            <!-- Axis titles -->\n            <text x=\"880\" y=\"340\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" transform=\"rotate(-90 880 340)\">Target</text>\n            <text x=\"1120\" y=\"190\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Source</text>\n            \n            <!-- Heatmap tensor shape -->\n            <text x=\"1120\" y=\"480\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">4x4</text>\n        </g>\n\n        <!-- Legend -->\n        <g id=\"legend\">\n            <rect x=\"1350\" y=\"200\" width=\"200\" height=\"280\" fill=\"#ffffff\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n            <text x=\"1450\" y=\"225\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Legend</text>\n            \n            <!-- Encoder -->\n            <rect x=\"1365\" y=\"240\" width=\"30\" height=\"20\" fill=\"url(#encoderGrad)\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"1\" rx=\"3\"/>\n            <text x=\"1405\" y=\"254\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Encoder RNN</text>\n            \n            <!-- Decoder -->\n            <rect x=\"1365\" y=\"270\" width=\"30\" height=\"20\" fill=\"url(#decoderGrad)\" stroke=\"#c0392b\" stroke-width=\"1\" rx=\"3\"/>\n            <text x=\"1405\" y=\"284\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Decoder RNN</text>\n            \n            <!-- Context -->\n            <rect x=\"1365\" y=\"300\" width=\"30\" height=\"20\" fill=\"url(#contextGrad)\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"1\" rx=\"3\"/>\n            <text x=\"1405\" y=\"314\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Context Vector</text>\n            \n            <!-- Tokens -->\n            <rect x=\"1365\" y=\"330\" width=\"30\" height=\"20\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"1\" rx=\"3\"/>\n            <text x=\"1405\" y=\"344\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Tokens</text>\n            \n            <!-- Hidden state arrow -->\n            <line x1=\"1365\" y1=\"365\" x2=\"1395\" y2=\"365\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <text x=\"1405\" y=\"369\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Hidden State</text>\n            \n            <!-- Attention arrow -->\n            <line x1=\"1365\" y1=\"385\" x2=\"1395\" y2=\"385\" stroke=\"#9b59b6\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#attentionArrow)\"/>\n            <text x=\"1405\" y=\"389\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Attention</text>\n            \n            <!-- High attention -->\n            <rect x=\"1365\" y=\"405\" width=\"20\" height=\"15\" fill=\"#d1ecf1\" stroke=\"#17a2b8\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"1395\" y=\"417\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">High Attn</text>\n            \n            <!-- Medium attention -->\n            <rect x=\"1365\" y=\"430\" width=\"20\" height=\"15\" fill=\"#fff3cd\" stroke=\"#f39c12\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n            <text x=\"1395\" y=\"442\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Med Attn</text>\n            \n            <!-- Low attention -->\n            <rect x=\"1365\" y=\"455\" width=\"20\" height=\"15\" fill=\"#f8d7da\" stroke=\"#e74c3c\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n            <text x=\"1395\" y=\"467\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Low Attn</text>\n        </g>\n\n        <!-- Additional annotations -->\n        <text x=\"300\" y=\"920\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">Source: French</text>\n        <text x=\"660\" y=\"100\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">Target: English</text>\n        \n        <!-- Tensor shapes -->\n        <text x=\"300\" y=\"900\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">4x256</text>\n        <text x=\"660\" y=\"80\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">4x256</text>\n    </svg>\n</body>\n</html>", "rv_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Seq2Seq with Attention</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 20px;\n            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n            background: #f8f9fa;\n            width: 1880px;\n            height: 1040px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        .title {\n            font-size: 32px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            text-align: center;\n            color: #2c3e50;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"title\">Seq2Seq with Attention</div>\n    \n    <svg width=\"1880\" height=\"980\" viewBox=\"0 0 1880 980\">\n        <!-- Definitions for gradients and patterns -->\n        <defs>\n            <linearGradient id=\"encoderGrad\" x1=\"0%\" y1=\"0%\" x2=\"100%\" y2=\"100%\">\n                <stop offset=\"0%\" style=\"stop-color:#3498db;stop-opacity:1\" />\n                <stop offset=\"100%\" style=\"stop-color:#2980b9;stop-opacity:1\" />\n            </linearGradient>\n            <linearGradient id=\"decoderGrad\" x1=\"0%\" y1=\"0%\" x2=\"100%\" y2=\"100%\">\n                <stop offset=\"0%\" style=\"stop-color:#e74c3c;stop-opacity:1\" />\n                <stop offset=\"100%\" style=\"stop-color:#c0392b;stop-opacity:1\" />\n            </linearGradient>\n            <linearGradient id=\"contextGrad\" x1=\"0%\" y1=\"0%\" x2=\"100%\" y2=\"100%\">\n                <stop offset=\"0%\" style=\"stop-color:#f39c12;stop-opacity:1\" />\n                <stop offset=\"100%\" style=\"stop-color:#e67e22;stop-opacity:1\" />\n            </linearGradient>\n            <marker id=\"arrowhead\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#34495e\" />\n            </marker>\n            <marker id=\"attentionArrow\" markerWidth=\"8\" markerHeight=\"6\" refX=\"7\" refY=\"3\" orient=\"auto\">\n                <polygon points=\"0 0, 8 3, 0 6\" fill=\"#9b59b6\" />\n            </marker>\n        </defs>\n\n        <!-- Encoder Section -->\n        <g id=\"encoder\">\n            <!-- Encoder Title -->\n            <text x=\"300\" y=\"680\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"18\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Encoder RNN</text>\n            \n            <!-- Source tokens -->\n            <rect x=\"80\" y=\"720\" width=\"60\" height=\"30\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n            <text x=\"110\" y=\"740\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">le</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"180\" y=\"720\" width=\"60\" height=\"30\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n            <text x=\"210\" y=\"740\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">chat</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"280\" y=\"720\" width=\"60\" height=\"30\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n            <text x=\"310\" y=\"740\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">est</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"380\" y=\"720\" width=\"60\" height=\"30\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n            <text x=\"410\" y=\"740\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">noir</text>\n            \n            <!-- Encoder cells -->\n            <rect x=\"80\" y=\"600\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" fill=\"url(#encoderGrad)\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n            <text x=\"110\" y=\"625\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">RNN</text>\n            <text x=\"110\" y=\"640\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"white\">h\u2081</text>\n            <text x=\"110\" y=\"655\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\">1\u00d7256</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"180\" y=\"600\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" fill=\"url(#encoderGrad)\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n            <text x=\"210\" y=\"625\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">RNN</text>\n            <text x=\"210\" y=\"640\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"white\">h\u2082</text>\n            <text x=\"210\" y=\"655\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\">1\u00d7256</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"280\" y=\"600\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" fill=\"url(#encoderGrad)\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n            <text x=\"310\" y=\"625\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">RNN</text>\n            <text x=\"310\" y=\"640\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"white\">h\u2083</text>\n            <text x=\"310\" y=\"655\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\">1\u00d7256</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"380\" y=\"600\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" fill=\"url(#encoderGrad)\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n            <text x=\"410\" y=\"625\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">RNN</text>\n            <text x=\"410\" y=\"640\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"white\">h\u2084</text>\n            <text x=\"410\" y=\"655\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\">1\u00d7256</text>\n            \n            <!-- Hidden state arrows -->\n            <line x1=\"140\" y1=\"630\" x2=\"170\" y2=\"630\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <line x1=\"240\" y1=\"630\" x2=\"270\" y2=\"630\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <line x1=\"340\" y1=\"630\" x2=\"370\" y2=\"630\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Input arrows -->\n            <line x1=\"110\" y1=\"720\" x2=\"110\" y2=\"670\" stroke=\"#7f8c8d\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <line x1=\"210\" y1=\"720\" x2=\"210\" y2=\"670\" stroke=\"#7f8c8d\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <line x1=\"310\" y1=\"720\" x2=\"310\" y2=\"670\" stroke=\"#7f8c8d\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <line x1=\"410\" y1=\"720\" x2=\"410\" y2=\"670\" stroke=\"#7f8c8d\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        </g>\n\n        <!-- Context Vector -->\n        <g id=\"context\">\n            <rect x=\"600\" y=\"400\" width=\"120\" height=\"80\" fill=\"url(#contextGrad)\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"3\" rx=\"10\"/>\n            <text x=\"660\" y=\"425\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">Context</text>\n            <text x=\"660\" y=\"445\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"white\">c\u208d = \u03a3 \u03b1\u208d\u1d62 h\u208d</text>\n            <text x=\"660\" y=\"465\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\">1\u00d7256</text>\n            \n            <!-- Attention arrows from encoder states -->\n            <line x1=\"110\" y1=\"600\" x2=\"620\" y2=\"480\" stroke=\"#9b59b6\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#attentionArrow)\" stroke-dasharray=\"5,3\"/>\n            <line x1=\"210\" y1=\"600\" x2=\"640\" y2=\"480\" stroke=\"#9b59b6\" stroke-width=\"4\" marker-end=\"url(#attentionArrow)\"/>\n            <line x1=\"310\" y1=\"600\" x2=\"660\" y2=\"480\" stroke=\"#9b59b6\" stroke-width=\"4\" marker-end=\"url(#attentionArrow)\"/>\n            <line x1=\"410\" y1=\"600\" x2=\"680\" y2=\"480\" stroke=\"#9b59b6\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#attentionArrow)\" stroke-dasharray=\"5,3\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Attention weights labels -->\n            <text x=\"350\" y=\"520\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#9b59b6\">\u03b1\u2081=0.1</text>\n            <text x=\"420\" y=\"500\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#9b59b6\">\u03b1\u2082=0.4</text>\n            <text x=\"480\" y=\"490\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#9b59b6\">\u03b1\u2083=0.4</text>\n            <text x=\"520\" y=\"500\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#9b59b6\">\u03b1\u2084=0.1</text>\n        </g>\n\n        <!-- Decoder Section -->\n        <g id=\"decoder\">\n            <!-- Decoder Title -->\n            <text x=\"660\" y=\"180\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"18\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Decoder RNN</text>\n            \n            <!-- Decoder cells -->\n            <rect x=\"480\" y=\"200\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" fill=\"url(#decoderGrad)\" stroke=\"#c0392b\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n            <text x=\"510\" y=\"225\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">RNN</text>\n            <text x=\"510\" y=\"240\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"white\">s\u2081</text>\n            <text x=\"510\" y=\"255\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\">1\u00d7256</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"580\" y=\"200\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" fill=\"url(#decoderGrad)\" stroke=\"#c0392b\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n            <text x=\"610\" y=\"225\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">RNN</text>\n            <text x=\"610\" y=\"240\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"white\">s\u2082</text>\n            <text x=\"610\" y=\"255\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\">1\u00d7256</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"680\" y=\"200\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" fill=\"url(#decoderGrad)\" stroke=\"#c0392b\" stroke-width=\"3\" rx=\"8\"/>\n            <text x=\"710\" y=\"225\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">RNN</text>\n            <text x=\"710\" y=\"240\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"white\">s\u2083</text>\n            <text x=\"710\" y=\"255\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\">1\u00d7256</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"780\" y=\"200\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" fill=\"url(#decoderGrad)\" stroke=\"#c0392b\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n            <text x=\"810\" y=\"225\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">RNN</text>\n            <text x=\"810\" y=\"240\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"white\">s\u2084</text>\n            <text x=\"810\" y=\"255\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\">1\u00d7256</text>\n            \n            <!-- Target tokens -->\n            <rect x=\"480\" y=\"120\" width=\"60\" height=\"30\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n            <text x=\"510\" y=\"140\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">the</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"580\" y=\"120\" width=\"60\" height=\"30\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n            <text x=\"610\" y=\"140\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">cat</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"680\" y=\"120\" width=\"60\" height=\"30\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n            <text x=\"710\" y=\"140\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">is</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"780\" y=\"120\" width=\"60\" height=\"30\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n            <text x=\"810\" y=\"140\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">black</text>\n            \n            <!-- Hidden state arrows -->\n            <line x1=\"540\" y1=\"230\" x2=\"570\" y2=\"230\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <line x1=\"640\" y1=\"230\" x2=\"670\" y2=\"230\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <line x1=\"740\" y1=\"230\" x2=\"770\" y2=\"230\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Output arrows -->\n            <line x1=\"510\" y1=\"200\" x2=\"510\" y2=\"160\" stroke=\"#7f8c8d\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <line x1=\"610\" y1=\"200\" x2=\"610\" y2=\"160\" stroke=\"#7f8c8d\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <line x1=\"710\" y1=\"200\" x2=\"710\" y2=\"160\" stroke=\"#7f8c8d\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <line x1=\"810\" y1=\"200\" x2=\"810\" y2=\"160\" stroke=\"#7f8c8d\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Context to current decoder -->\n            <line x1=\"660\" y1=\"400\" x2=\"710\" y2=\"270\" stroke=\"#f39c12\" stroke-width=\"4\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <text x=\"680\" y=\"340\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#f39c12\" font-weight=\"bold\">Current Step</text>\n        </g>\n\n        <!-- Attention Heatmap -->\n        <g id=\"heatmap\">\n            <text x=\"1200\" y=\"180\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"18\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Attention Alignment</text>\n            \n            <!-- Heatmap grid -->\n            <rect x=\"1050\" y=\"220\" width=\